Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:22.71,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}だがらあなたはそのままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I & I = You & I
